race.comment: BURRINGBAR REBEL (1) is better than last start when sixth (25.95) from Box 6 at Q Lakeside over 457m. Ready to return to form. DASHING DENNIS (8) finished a 0.8 lengths second last start over 350m at Grafton in a quick 19.99. Harder here but expected to measure up. IOMMI (2) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Finished in the minors latest when second (23.55) at this track and may be close to breaking through. Yet to score from this box but has never missed the frame in two starts. Will give a great sight again. SWEETEST SMILE (6) comes off a (23.15) win last time, scoring by 6 lengths in a Grade 5 over 411m at this track. Has already won two times from this draw.
